<br>
Regardless of where you solo - and this is largely governed by where you can find elemental mobs - there will be a lot of deaths while you get a feel for charm soloing in BoT. Ask any enchanter who has done it. You would benefit by having a cleric friend or access to a cleric bot for resses - you *will* make a lot of corpses to begin with.<br>
